  "original_title": "\u0d9c\u0ddd\u0da8\u0dcf \u0d9c\u0ddd \u0d9c\u0db8\u0da7 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3\u0db8 \u0d9c\u0dd0\u0db1 \u0dc0\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca \u0db6\u0daf\u0dcf\u0daf\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A debate about the attack on Gota Go village on Wednesday",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A debate regarding the evacuation of the protesters from the Colombo Golf Course \"Gota Go Village\" protest site is scheduled to be held in Parliament tomorrow (27).",
        "The main organizer of the opposition, MP Lakshman Kiriella, requested the Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardena yesterday (23) to convene the Parliament today (25) to discuss the matter.",
        "As it is practically difficult to convene the parliament today and summon the MPs due to the fuel issue, the government intends to debate the same issue when the parliament meets tomorrow, Wednesday, to pass the emergency law gazette notification.",
        "Prior to this, the Committee on Parliamentary Affairs had decided to pass the gazette notification on the emergency law for the next day's meeting of Parliament.",
        "Lakshman Kiriella, the main organizer of the opposition, said that it is very important to have a dialogue about it as it is an illegal and undemocratic act to beat and kick out the activists."
      ],
